Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:05.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:08.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:12.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy the miracle that is going \Nto happen under the moonlight tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:24.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! This isn't it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:27.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Another one I gotta return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:48.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:50.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:51.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:54.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I'm all ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:00:59.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Magic tricks and magic spells(Mah≈ç)  \Ncan both be considered "magic" in English,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:01.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but they're completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:03.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Magic spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:06.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you know the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:14.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:18.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know there's \Nno such thing as {\i1}real{\i0} magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:27.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mirror, mirror, on the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:33.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,who's the fairest of them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:37.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That would be you, Akako-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:41.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Men all over the world are enamored of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:46.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Except for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh? And who might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:54.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:02.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:38.01,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)}Scarlet Seduction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:38.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaito, don't you want something sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Something sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. For instance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aoko, have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:49.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Forgotten what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:52.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Back when I had that cavity...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:56.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at that bulging cheek! \NWhat a weird face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:58.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:01.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You laughed! So you think I'm \Ngonna fall for it now, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:04.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's February 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:09.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All girls bring chocolate to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the day when we give it to boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:17.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure nobody else \Nwould give you any,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm only giving it to you \Nbecause I feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:25.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Besides, there's a romantic \Nfull moon out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:29.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And if it snows, we'll have \Na white Valentine's day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Uh, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:33.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? Keiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito-kun ran off thataway with \Na big grin plastered on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:40.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're gonna give that \Nchocolate to him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You vixen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Who would give that guy chocolate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:46.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're lucky to have someone \Nto give it to, Aoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I told you I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:53.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That girl is monopolizing all the other guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:05:00.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Koizumi Akako, who just \Nstarted here a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-sama, give me chocolate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Me too! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't push, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll give you what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:16.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She acts like she's a queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:22.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But Akako-chan really is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:27.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Every single man in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:31.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,is wrapped around my little finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at all the loot I got!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:37.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This one's from Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This one's from Sakura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And this is from Ayano-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:42.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:47.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aoko, why is everyone \Ngiving me chocolate today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:49.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As I was saying, today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:52.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I never \Ncome to school on February 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Last year, I had a terrible cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:59.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The year before, I was hospitalized with \Na broken ankle after a skating accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:06.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I always thought it was an unlucky day, \Nnever knowing what I was missin' out on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:11.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-chan! Give me chocolate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:17.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kaito?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Another one of Kaito's tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:24.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's no trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who is this girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:30.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you want my chocolate, you'll \Nhave to dump all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:34.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right! You're \Nbeing rude to Akako-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see. Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He doesn't {\i1}need{\i0} my chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's like snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone, take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, you brought chocolate too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:14.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not for you, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of {\i1}course{\i0} you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:23.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief is the \Nonly one who can resist me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unless {\i1}he's{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aoko, have you seen my hankie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't seen your stupid hankie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then let me borrow you a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:44.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're rotten to the core!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:50.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll expose your other identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is everything ready for the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:28.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It is all set, Akako-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll never get over how ugly you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:45.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. And you are always \Nbeautiful, Akako-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:51.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You are the rightful heir to red magic. You \Nshould become the empress of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:55.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Silence! I'm tired of hearing you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:57.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, I shall begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:00.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As you wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dragon's whisker, mermaid's tear, \Neyeball of a {\i1}kappa{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:13.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...I give you this handkerchief, \Nsymbolizing Kaito Kuroba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It won't be long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:27.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You shall soon be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.53,Signs,,0,0,0,,Blue Parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:37.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:42.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess February 14th is an \Nunlucky day for me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:47.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, \Nit's been a sweet day for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:51.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I've got \Na feeling of foreboding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I just hope I don't get injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:56.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:10:00.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you believe in real magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Real" magic does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:08.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:12.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Another term for it would be "sorcery."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:16.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Different kinds of sorcery \Nhave color designations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:20.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There are black magic, white magic,\N blue magic, red magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Red magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:26.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorcerers are the mortal \Nenemies of us magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:30.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We have been at odds with each other \Nsince ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:37.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Some of them despise us, and \Nconsider what we do "fake magic."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:39.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,D-Despise us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:44.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, there's \Na full moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:48.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's long been said that the full moon \Nis an omen of bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:52.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young Master, please watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:14.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even though I sent out advance notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You fell for one of the \Noldest tricks in the book!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Knockout gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:44.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Find him! He can't have gone far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:52.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're the ones who fall for old tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:55.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But this is no good... I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:01.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fool. Did you really \Nthink you could get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:04.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,C-Can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come to me, Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:15.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Or rather, Kaito Kuroba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:18.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now! Grab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:19.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:23.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll release you from your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:26.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So come to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:54.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:58.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I had a bad feeling about tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:01.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But don't worry. I'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's not that, Jii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They're not our enemies tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come to me, Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,J-Jii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:23.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Quickly... You're almost here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:26.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know who the hell you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:29.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but at least your night flight woke me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:33.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll save you from your torments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:49.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, \Nmy ostentatious rascal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:56.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This time, {\i1}you're{\i0} going to be the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:14:01.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You see, I'm going to steal your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:10.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll catch cold in that outfit, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:15.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you supposed to be a gentleman now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:17.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:21.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't tease an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:23.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So, hand over that doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A-A magic circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is... red magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought this would finally be \Nthe year I could give it to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,God's mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:23.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your body already belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:26.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, become my servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:30.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you sure are a spoiled young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:34.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Laugh while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:49.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Again, become my servant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hot! It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:16:01.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid. You want to escape \Nthat agony, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:05.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then eat this chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:08.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:09.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:16.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This time you'll accept my red feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:18.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:24.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Although after receiving it,\N your heart will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:27.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...mine for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Eat it, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:31.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young lady, your magic \Ndoesn't work on me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:42.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Snow put out my magic circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,White Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the magic of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You mean the trick up your sleeve, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:17.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You always use magic tricks to \Nescape when you're in a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:20.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But in the end, they're all a fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They just fool people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:28.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My magic is real! The effects really happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:32.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You mean to escape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:42.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Certainly, the magic I perform fools people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But everyone who sees it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:46.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:58.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They enjoy being fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the difference between \Nyour magic and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:09.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Stealing people's hearts \Nthrough sorcery is just sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:15.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But that's how we witches operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's telling lies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:24.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:28.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, you are. You're lying to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:33.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young lady, you can't fool \NKid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:40.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can see the beautiful gem lying \Ndeep within your frozen heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...Akako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:49.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Farewell, cute sorceress.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,M-My lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:06.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know. If a witch sheds a tear,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:09.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,she'll lose her magic power forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:28.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:39.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You still have that chocolate \Nfrom yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:42.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:45.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That only means something if \NI give it out on Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I ate it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:54.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is the chocolate from...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not the same one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:57.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:59.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:04.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito Kuroba...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:11.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As a sorceress and magician, we share the \Nbond of knowing each other's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:15.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time, I {\i1}will{\i0} make you mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:20.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:21.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:24.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Akako-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:32.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:40.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, let's meet again \Nunder the falling snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:43.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See you next illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:23.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm usually at the top of my game \Nwhen it comes to thieving and magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.57,0:23:25.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but once in a while, \Nthings don't go as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:27.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This town has had a clock tower \Nfor many years now,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:30.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and my target is the \Ndiamond-encrusted hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:33.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but somebody's seeing through \Nmy every move?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.75,0:23:36.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's definitely not old man Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:38.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:43.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,Black Star
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.92,0:23:43.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:\N Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.09,0:23:46.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.30,0:23:48.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the illusion!
